data.title: Springside Bitz N' Bytes Summer 2014
data.meta_description: Springside Bitz n' Bytes summer 2014 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The Springside 4-H Beef Club members visited a local feedlot to learn more about feeding cattle from the owners. They thanked the family and staff for sharing their knowledge and the Yorkton Co-op for providing lunch. The club members are preparing their project calves for the upcoming 4-H Regional Show and Sale by learning to develop proper feeding rations to optimize weight gain.
